        <num>CC 2891</num>
        <heading>LOAN</heading>
        <content>
          <p>TITLE XII.  LOAN
CHAPTER 1.  LOAN FOR USE (COMMODATUM)
Art. 2891.  Loan for use; definition
The loan for use is a gratuitous contract by which a person, the lender, delivers a nonconsumable thing to another, the borrower, for him to use and return.</p>
